{
  "texts": [
    "The integration of retrieval mechanisms helps to mitigate the limitations of static training data, enabling the model to dynamically access information that may not have been included in its training corpus.",
    "Consequently, RAG holds significant potential for addressing the challenges associated with factual inaccuracy in LLMs.The objective of this paper is to explore the implementation and efficacy of augmenting LLMs with a reverse proxy-style RAG to achieve higher factual accuracy.",
    "Specifically, the study focuses on the open-source Llama 3 model with 7B parameters, referred to as Llama.",
    "By augmenting Llama with RAG, the research aims to demonstrate that the integration of retrieval mechanisms can significantly enhance the model's factual accuracy.",
    "The contributions of this paper are threefold."
  ]
}